data.name: Additional Information
data.description: This allows you to add extra information for your members.  Any fields added here will be added to all members.

config.settings_summary: Photos & medical details can require additional consent depending on your lawful processing mechanism.  You can store/collect consents through OSM (and optionally My.SCOUT).  Please select ONE photographic consent option that is the closest match to your requirements (as giving parents to choose any of the options would make it impractical to take photos).  All changes to these fields will be stored in the member's history.

I give consent for photos/videos of my child to be taken, stored and shared internally in the meeting location, local press, Scout websites and social media. I understand that if I later withdraw consent, previously published photos will not be able to be removed. (Regardless of this consent, the group/unit is not responsible for photos taken by other parties.)
